Also, every time you purchase a Turtle product, part of the proceeds go towards protecting and conserving turtles. This is part of the Save Turtle project created in collaboration with WWF and Wildlife Society of Orissa.

Length
117 cm

Made of leather with a textured finish for absolute durability, comfort and style
Stylish buckle clasp and holes to customise Fit
Metal brand tab embossed on the side of the buckle

Care
Wipe surface with a clean, dry cloth to remove dust
Use a leather conditioner to maintain belt quality if necessary
